### Workflow Engine API Examples
### Use with REST Client extensions like VS Code REST Client

# Set base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Get All Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/templates

### 2. Get Templates by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/templates?category=video_content

### 3. Search Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/search?q=youtube

### 4. Get Specific Template
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/templates/youtube-script-generator

### 5. Create Custom Template
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/templates
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Custom Blog Post Generator",
  "description": "Generates blog posts with custom structure",
  "category": "content_marketing",
  "tags": ["blog", "content", "writing"],
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "analyze_topic",
      "type": "analyze_input",
      "name": "Analyze Topic",
      "order": 0,
      "dependencies": [],
      "config": {
        "analysisType": "content",
        "focus": "blog_writing"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "structure_content",
      "type": "breakdown_structure",
      "name": "Structure Content",
      "order": 1,
      "dependencies": ["analyze_topic"],
      "config": {
        "structureType": "article"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "generate_content",
      "type": "generate_output",
      "name": "Generate Content",
      "order": 2,
      "dependencies": ["structure_content"],
      "config": {
        "outputType": "article",
        "articleStyle": "engaging"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "refine_content",
      "type": "refine_output",
      "name": "Refine Content",
      "order": 3,
      "dependencies": ["generate_content"],
      "config": {
        "refinementType": "clarity_readability"
      }
    }
  ],
  "inputSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "required": ["topic"],
    "properties": {
      "topic": { "type": "string" },
      "tone": { "type": "string" },
      "wordCount": { "type": "number" }
    }
  }
}

### 6. Validate Template
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/templates/validate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test Template",
  "category": "test",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "step1",
      "type": "analyze_input",
      "name": "First Step",
      "order": 0,
      "dependencies": []
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Execute YouTube Script Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/execute/youtube-script-generator
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "topic": "10 AI Tools That Will Change Your Life in 2024",
    "duration": "12 minutes",
    "style": "educational",
    "targetAudience": "tech enthusiasts",
    "keywords": ["AI", "tools", "2024", "technology"],
    "callToAction": "Subscribe for more AI content!"
  },
  "config": {
    "optimizeForSEO": true
  }
}

### 8. Execute SEO Article Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/execute/seo-article-generator
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "topic": "The Future of Artificial Intelligence in Healthcare",
    "keywords": ["AI", "healthcare", "future", "medicine", "technology"],
    "targetAudience": "healthcare professionals",
    "articleLength": "long",
    "tone": "professional",
    "primaryKeyword": "AI in healthcare",
    "wordCount": 2000,
    "includeMetaDescription": true
  }
}

### 9. Execute Ad Copy Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/execute/ad-copy-generator
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "product": "AI-Powered Project Management Tool",
    "audience": "Small business owners and project managers",
    "adType": "social_media",
    "tone": "professional",
    "uniqueSellingProposition": "Automate your project management with AI",
