Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "",
  "category": "",
  "steps": []
}

### 25. Error Handling Test - Invalid Execution
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/execute/invalid-template-id
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "test": "data"
  }
}

