}

### 27. Get Template Variants
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/templates?category=video_content

### 28. Execute with Custom Configuration
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow-engine/execute/youtube-script-generator
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "input": {
    "topic": "Advanced JavaScript Techniques",
    "duration": "20 minutes",
    "style": "tutorial",
    "targetAudience": "experienced developers"
  },
  "config": {
    "includeTimestamps": true,
    "optimizeForSEO": true,
    "customStyle": "technical"
  }
}
